---
title: Caribbean Black Bean & Veggie Pie with Coconut Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing plant-based pie! A coconutty, Caribbean-spiced bean filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.

*Unfortunately, this
week's lentils were in
short supply, so we've
replaced them with black
beans. Don't worry, the
recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
